{"tid":144720,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［大狗撚］有冇養大狗既巴絲預過咁既情況","createTime":"2017-03-05T15:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T20:01:46.000Z","uid":88962,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"866b9682ba93ad0cd7f91dda1da783c3aab0bb5a","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"事源我地屋企收養左隻唐狗女 中至大size <br />\n我懷疑個衰妹有種族歧視<br />\n個衰妹見到其他狗無野 但一見親poodle就想咬 <br />\n之前有請工人 個仆街工人放繩比佢周圍走 <br />\n<br />\n利申：收養之前已經一早話左比個仆街工人知要佢一定要拖繩 因為咁撚大隻狗好危險<br />\n<br />\n有一次條仆街唔聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放左繩等佢痾屎 <br />\n搞到咬到人地隻toy poodle要聯針<br />\n利申：隻poodle<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇拖繩</span></span><br />\n我地管理狗隻（工人）不善 賠償係好應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都係愛狗之人<br />\n我見到隻狗仔咁大個傷口 我都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拿拿聲同埋佢個主人一齊落去睇獸醫 <br />\n<br />\n佢依家都好番哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n依家個工人冇做啦 今晚我個妹出去扔垃圾 帶埋隻狗出一出痾尿啦 諗住出去2分鐘 就冇同佢戴口罩 但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有拖繩</span></span><br />\n（各位巴絲唔好打面）<br />\n<br />\n又有另一隻<span style=\"color: blue;\">poodle</span>出現 <br />\n皆因我地知道隻衰狗咁衰<br />\n我妹已經拖實哂佢 <br />\n仲大大聲叫佢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人唔好比隻狗過尼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢隻狗係無拖繩既！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但佢唔聽 冇叫住佢隻狗 <br />\n我隻狗想咬佢 但根本冇咬到<br />\n佢係咁發難炸話要驗傷又話盛<br />\n我個妹又低b唔識處理<br />\n最尾我咁岩番尼路過見到條友係咁鬧我個妹 <br />\n我上前問咩事 我個妹同我講啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「係咪依家你隻狗咬到我隻狗 我仲要同你道歉啊？報警囉！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「先生，我地隻狗嚇親你隻狗唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n佢可能見我女仔諗住恰我，咬住唔放，大大聲鬧我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「你地都唔識教狗咖，你隻狗會咬狗就同佢戴口罩啦。」<br />\n<br />\n我諗住 唉算啦 快d say sorry番屋企訓覺算。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「先生，係我地唔岩，對唔住。」<br />\n<br />\n點知粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲咬住唔放<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「你地唔識教就唔好學人養狗啦。」<br />\n<br />\n今次真係佛都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「先生，其實你自己隻狗都無拖繩，唔好話見到其他狗啦，唔拖繩原本就係好危險咖。各何況我地已經警吿左你唔好比佢埋你，但你都冇叫佢番尼。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「我緊係唔洗拖繩啦，我隻狗咁乖...」<br />\n<br />\n都未講完，佢隻狗就自己衝出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 掛住鬧我地根本無睇住隻狗。我睇到即刻話佢知，我仲緊張過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，遲多2秒就有架大貨車經過。嚇撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「你睇下，唔拖繩真係好危險咖。頭先差d出事，好彩我睇到咋。」<br />\n<br />\n然後粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 面矇矇咁打左佢隻狗一下 走左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但都奉勸各位巴絲放狗[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">記得拖繩</span>[/size=6<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴絲會覺得我惡人先吿狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ？究竟係我錯定佢錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9a4c6b1bf3bb116c1608e3430a2be63097b915","tid":144720,"uid":52742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"屌 有時有啲人就係咁撚仆街 <br />\n我講個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35af97ef333a7fdd5298ce8d415d35aadb6cb66b","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 有時有啲人就係咁撚仆街 <br />\n我講個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩唔係講我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補充資料：粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都好慘咖 我諗佢成三十歲 都仲矮過我差唔多半個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係祝佢快高長大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：我身高158"},{"pid":"91cf48fb16ae8a4a788ce74e08b40340a7ef5099","tid":144720,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下你隻狗咩樣"},{"pid":"a3ad09119ac12f3f2524846bf0ca33b2eb1b17ec","tid":144720,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"直頭戴口罩先出街啦"},{"pid":"e73e04c0947869c09856031e355397d5d7f8d992","tid":144720,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"種族歧視呢個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5553da6f7e97f1b031a887f6944aedc2e64d96a0","tid":144720,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"我識人個頭係細鬈啡色爆炸頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻poodle 個頭咁<br />\n樓主隻狗會唔會認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcd996e0754c9e20f2ca8f58f57851487398771","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直頭戴口罩先出街啦</blockquote><br />\n以後唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係諗住轉頭就番屋企所以先冇戴 同埋見佢戴左好唔舒服 心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b52afa308872759d0c40850f96cff722984e679","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下你隻狗咩樣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c2fdd5b4753506d73b11627e284ddce845c6a0b9","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下你隻狗咩樣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/021138_33d9850d85c2fa3ac23a343c7be0ac53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F021138_33d9850d85c2fa3ac23a343c7be0ac53.jpg&h=185f9144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似唔似拉多/金毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c12cafe19784872c00ef22764cc16b27b41c282","tid":144720,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"咬到就點都唔岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩好拗"},{"pid":"5be99b8850515a00b3a7b90dfa8c74d9d6ddfad0","tid":144720,"uid":43450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"其實冇分大狗細狗<br />\n岀親去冇拖繩就係唔岩<br />\n理撚得你隻狗有幾乖<br />\n保障自己保障人地<br />\n有咩事隻狗嚇一嚇衝岀馬路真係後悔都冇用<br />\n絲打我撐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養過大狗 而家養細狗<br />\n我隻狗都都係種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n專門歧視法國鬥牛呢一類<br />\n見親到「胡」到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2f6f8b7dcfd54c730a7205f16e7902c8f5d9e0","tid":144720,"uid":5309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"大家都有責任 <br />\n你隻狗應該帶口罩 個個人都應該拖繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221e977dd0b3455718d2ef1a4237f3a51d430112","tid":144720,"uid":11205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:07:54.000Z","msg":"我放親兩隻雪橇啲人就覺得成隻怪獸咁 <br />\n養大狗習慣左比人岐視"},{"pid":"571d2d0d7d4c0b54a8ee1e5919d615bda3578212","tid":144720,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T20:56:17.000Z","msg":"我都養緊<br />\nd狗大得好快 依加9個月"},{"pid":"e76cadb45293b2bf9f84374363a57022066df3cf","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咬到就點都唔岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩好拗</blockquote><br />\n冇咬到啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea6fa788d99b416f1feffab96ccb1a69854a0c0","tid":144720,"uid":22147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"保障自己同狗狗幫佢帶口罩啦 好多人都歧視唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a09a8b4cae9bc6bf086d9a4aaea92b128e6f20","tid":144720,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"既然你都知你隻狗會咬Poodle 就戴返個口罩啦 養Poodle嘅人都幾多 你隻狗無咬 但成日咁樣嚇一嚇啲狗仔 對佢哋心理都會造成影響 當然 粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔拖繩就點都唔啱<br />\n<br />\n利申：養緊Poodle 試過出街畀隻大隻嘅唐狗嚇親 大家都有用繩 佢隻狗係咁吠 係咁想撲埋嚟 搞到我隻Poodle而家好撚細膽 郁啲就吠 見到陌生人行得太埋就吠 就算喺屋企 屋企人喺廁所出嚟 開門大力咗啲都吠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我睇到佢都心痛 成日叫佢唔使驚 我都努力保護佢 而家喺街見到狗都叫啲人唔好過嚟"},{"pid":"f3f0ea2771cb285cdf3b257e6e7642330b923719","tid":144720,"uid":53159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"我嗰隻係北京，有時夜媽媽12點幾放佢先夠膽唔用繩俾佢跑吓，其餘時間一定用繩,條mk仔一見到其他狗就撩事鬥非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd0bd6a98b8c0a3b7db9f67a345ed0a4bd55255","tid":144720,"uid":70492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"我隻哥基見親牧羊都吠到癲，可能妒忌佢長腿過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e2343ac98f3db1b1066f0cdbf429ed6fe42b4","tid":144720,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"兩個都有錯, 不過對方比你多一粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4986958c43a60fe97c1f75a0b3b109598eb0fc1a","tid":144720,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既然你都知你隻狗會咬Poodle 就戴返個口罩啦 養Poodle嘅人都幾多 你隻狗無咬 但成日咁樣嚇一嚇啲狗仔 對佢哋心理都會造成影響 當然 粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔拖繩就點都唔啱<br />\n<br />\n利申：養緊Poodle 試過出街畀隻大隻嘅唐狗嚇親 大家都有用繩 佢隻狗係咁吠 係咁想撲埋嚟 搞到我隻Poodle而家好撚細膽 郁啲就吠 見到陌生人行得太埋就吠 就算喺屋企 屋企人喺廁所出嚟 開